## Outputs

Write to `econ-sims/{slug}/counterfactuals/{intervention-slug}/`:

| File | Contents |
|------|----------|
| `HYPOTHESIS.md` | Hypothesis, intervention spec, outcome formula, pre-registered decision rule |
| `RUNS.md` | Seed scheme, paired-run partition, sensitivity grid, parallelism plan, compute budget |
| `RESULTS.md` | Headline tables, confidence bands, probability-of-direction |
| `SENSITIVITY.md` | Sweep table, robustness verdict, parameter ranking, regime-break check |
| `REPORT.md` | Structured publishable report; the gate artifact |

Also append to `.gstack/decisions/counterfactual-{slug}-{intervention-slug}.md`
the intervention rationale, the ensemble-size choice rationale, and any
pre-registration deviations (which should be near zero — pre-registration is
binding).

